Next, you need to complete your profile.   1) You should be on a screen with a dialogue box, ready for you to write things in it. Up the top, there's the "back to dashboard" button - click it.   2) you'll see your blog listed in the "blogs" box. On the right, there's "edit profile". Click it.   3) DO NOT select "show my real name". DO enter your real name.  Worry about adding a picture later. add your IM name if you like. Remember that birthdays are written american style (mm/dd/yyyy).